{"tid":1906914,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"日本代購被人刪coupon，有冇辦法搵返個記錄","createTime":"2020-03-02T09:04:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T09:04:29.000Z","uid":168564,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bdcfdec86fb99f86a194bd246a05563e8b6ed9f8","tid":1906914,"uid":168564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T09:04:29.000Z","msg":"早幾日見到之前用開個日本代購有張2442JPY運費 coupon，有啲心動琴日就搵佢哋代購。<br />\n<br />\n到咗今朝，見到張coupon已經比佢哋De咗。<br />\n明明到期日喺27.02-07.03<br />\n但佢哋嗰邊直接炸死，話完全冇呢張coupon存在。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kukFyhx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkukFyhx.jpg&h=c4efd3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請問一下各位有冇辦法搵返個記錄出嚟？<br />\n我冇de Cookie同瀏覽記錄<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ssyf6CL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fssyf6CL.jpg&h=39cccf0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nThanks"}]}